## Technology Stack

| Category | Technology | Notes |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **Runtime** | Bun | JavaScript/TypeScript runtime |
| **Framework** | Next.js 16 | App Router, Turbopack |
| **UI Library** | React 19 | Server and Client Components |
| **Language** | TypeScript 5.8 | tsgo (TypeScript native preview) |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS | Utility-first CSS |
| **Animation** | GSAP + Lenis | Scroll animations, smooth scroll |
| **Linting** | oxlint | Fast linter |
| **Formatting** | oxfmt | Fast formatter |
| **Type checking** | tsgo | TypeScript native preview compiler |
| **Testing** | Bun test runner + Playwright | Unit/integration + E2E |
| **Dead code** | Knip | Unused exports/imports detection |

## Package Management

- **Use `bun`** for all dependency management. Do NOT use `npm`, `pnpm`, or `yarn`.
